dct_title_s: Salisburgensis iurisdictionis, locorumque vicinorum vera descriptio
dct_description_sm: Map of area around Salzburg, Austria with relief shown pictorially. "Cum priuilegio." Inset: Urbis Salisburgensis genuina descriptio; bird's-eye view of Salzburg. From: Theatrum, oder, Schawbuch des Erdtkreys ... In Antorff [Antwerp] : Bey Christoffel Plantin, in Verlegung Abraham Örtell, 1580. German text on verso with caption title: Das Bischthumb Saltzburg; p. 51. Historic Maps copy has no. 51 on verso altered in ms. to 54.
